{"tid":1247602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"LIHKG個Hosting係百度既Strategic Partnership!!","createTime":"2019-06-21T07:14:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T13:13:50.000Z","uid":88032,"like":17,"dislike":90,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"5e8ec290f00bdefdf37b542d0603ec7dadf8d5b3","tid":1247602,"uid":88032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T07:14:21.000Z","msg":"支納維基個搞手係中國去加拿大讀書既留學生<br />\n共產黨控制住佢老母，迫個搞手交成個網站比共產黨<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.zhina.wiki/%E6%94%AF%E7%BA%B3%E7%BB%B4%E5%9F%BA:%E9%A6%96%E9%A1%B5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhina.wiki%2F%25E6%2594%25AF%25E7%25BA%25B3%25E7%25BB%25B4%25E5%259F%25BA%3A%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%25A1%25B5&d=ciqixHjE7SQ%2Bh8bl84MOe29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=2cb61ced\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhina.wiki/%E6%94%AF%E7%BA%B3%E7%BB%B4%E5%9F%BA:%E9%A6%96%E9%A1%B5</a><br />\n共產黨無即刻熄哂成個網，反而利用左佢做左釣魚網站，邊個人係大陸上支納維基，就約邊個飲茶<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wCFp3L4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwCFp3L4.png&h=3c5f8c6a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pfFmmxK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpfFmmxK.jpg&h=4e4cfb87&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TYsWUSL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTYsWUSL.jpg&h=8d87b179&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KywkB55.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKywkB55.png&h=0b2070a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而支納維基網同LIHKG同樣都係用美國Cloudflare到做Hosting既<br />\n一查Cloudflare個底<br />\nWebsite security company Cloudflare is preparing for a $3.5 billion IPO<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2018/10/23/cloudflare-prepares-for-3-billion-ipo.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2018%2F10%2F23%2Fcloudflare-prepares-for-3-billion-ipo.html&d=ciqixHjE7SQ%2Bh8bl84MOe29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=a46d98af\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2018/10/23/cloudflare-prepares-for-3-billion-ipo.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ar5QZj0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAr5QZj0.png&h=f9316eb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCloudflare and Baidu Announce Strategic Partnership to Help Build a Better Internet<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cloudflare.com/press-releases/2015/cloudflare-and-baidu-announce-strategic-partnership-to-help-build-a-better-internet/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cloudflare.com%2Fpress-releases%2F2015%2Fcloudflare-and-baidu-announce-strategic-partnership-to-help-build-a-better-internet%2F&d=ciqixHjE7SQ%2Bh8bl84MOe29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=a6ac715b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cloudflare.com/press-releases/2015/cloudflare-and-baidu-announce-strategic-partnership-to-help-build-a-better-internet/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y89Vq0o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY89Vq0o.png&h=dbfe31c8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nCloudflare 2015年就已經係百度既Strategic Partner，百度仲入哂股等Cloudflare上IPO抽水<br />\n既然共產黨可以利用Cloudflare將支納維基變成釣魚網站<br />\n咁LIHKG<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ebcfcc09852ff91f69d5f1a17029b888ee5816d","tid":1247602,"uid":42202,"like":78,"dislike":1,"score":77,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T07:15:42.000Z","msg":"on9 唔用 cloudflare 用乜撚野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bad1e00812dbdedb8430757503aa66dca1406fd","tid":1247602,"uid":150666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T07:15:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e90b2899bf8f2b0924970d80365179abdbc8ce96","tid":1247602,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T07:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=